input_text.Response A: Expand your storage space with the Acrimet Wall-mounted Modular File Holder!  This modern, sturdy organizer is designed to hold letter sized folders and documents, and can easily be expanded to suit your storage needs.  The modular design allows you to add additional holders as needed, and the smoke color finish complements any modern decor.  Includes wall hangers for easy installation.  Set of 2.
input_text.Response B: Keep your files organized and easy to access with the Acrimet Wall-mounted Modular File Holder. This set comes with two holders, each with a modern, modular design that is easy to expand to fit your needs. The holders are also easy to install, with all the necessary wall hangers included. The smoke-colored holders are made of modern, strong and sturdy construction, and they will look great in any office or home.
